title: Mark Hamill Records Donald Trump’s Obama Wire Tapping Tweets in the Villainous Voice of The Joker
text:
Mark Hamill is back as The Trumpster reading Donald Trump’s tweets accusing Obama of wire tapping in the villainous voice of The Joker .
When in doubt-Blame Obama! #ProjectionParadeOfDiabolicalDeceptiveDeflection https://t.co/9Heqen4blQ pic.twitter.com/5sLzgSuQ9F 
— Mark Hamill (@HamillHimself) March 7, 2017
